                                    partially-legible <material>blue</material> circular seal
                                    impression, with a central inscription stacked in three lines
                                    double-ruled, surrounded by four cartouches, single ruled, one
                                    of which clearly names former owner <persName role="fmo seal"
                                        ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/2457671" key="person_2457671"
                                        >Jibrā'īl bin Yūsuf al-Mukhalla‘ (d. 1851)</persName>,
                                    albeit posthumously dated <date calendar="#Gregorian"
                                        when="1877">1877</date>.</p>
                                <p><dimensions type="seal" unit="mm" subtype="diameter">
